Interface Func3<INPUT1,INPUT2,INPUT3,OUTPUT>

  • Type Parameters:
    INPUT1 - the first input data type.
    INPUT2 - the second input data type.
    INPUT3 - the third input data type.
    OUTPUT - the output data type.
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface Func3<INPUT1,INPUT2,INPUT3,OUTPUT>
    Function of three parameters.
